column1: Synthetic Community : The synthetic community to which the isolate was gavaged with
16S Sanger Sequencing BLAST Annotation: All isolates were 16SU Sanger sequenced, and this was the top BLAST hit for each isolate
Isolation source: Dictates whether the isolate was from human or mouse, and which intestinal region
16S MiSeq Sequencing Name: After the isoalte was grown for the second mouse gavage, it was sent for 16S MiSeq sequencing to assess purity. This indicates the name of the sequencing sample
ASV Relative Abundace, ASV Genus, ASV Species: The relative abundance of an ASV within that sample and its Genus and Species annotation
